nps
===

This is an implementation of SUSv4 'ps', and a compatible 'top', for
Linux.

* Installation

    ./configure
    make
    sudo make install

See 'INSTALL' for generic instructions

* Documentation

    nps --help
    nps --help-format
    man nps

    nps-top --help
    man nps-top

* Use

    nps
    nps -ef
    nps-top

    alias ps=nps
    alias top=nps-top # if you like them more than the system versions

* Maintainer

Please send bug reports to:
  Richard Kettlewell <rjk@greenend.org.uk>

